         <div type="edition" xml:lang="ocm-Latn" rendition="class:83233 maturity:00000">
					 <p>
						 <lb n="1"/>siddhaM<g type="spiralR"/> nī yāṄ nāga puÑ putauV ya UrāṄ spūY di ko
						 <lb n="2"/>kuruN ko jmāY labuḥ nari svarggaḥ ya UrāṄ paribhū d<unclear>i</unclear> ko
						 <lb n="3"/>kuruN saribū thūN ko davaM di naraka dṅaN tijūḥ kulo ko
					 </p>
         </div>
         <div type="apparatus">
               <listApp>
								 <app loc="1">
	 								 <lem>nī</lem>
	 								 <rdg source="bib:Coedes1939_01">ni</rdg>
	 							</app>
								<app loc="1">
									<lem>yāṄ</lem>
									<rdg source="bib:Coedes1939_01">yaṄ</rdg>
							 </app>
               </listApp>
         </div>
				 <div type="translation">
					 <p n="1-3">Success! This is the divine serpent of the king.
						 People who are gentle to this lord <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ko kurun</foreign></supplied>, they <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ko</foreign></supplied> shall not fall from heaven. People who insult this lord, a thousand years they suffer from fever in hell with their seven generations of descendants.</p>
				 </div>
				 <div type="translation" xml:lang="fra" source="bib:Coedes1937-1966_01">
					 <p n="1-3">Succès ! Ceci est le saint <foreign>nāga</foreign> du roi. Quiconque le traite doucement....... des joyaux tombent ciel ; quiconque l'insulte...... pendant 1000 années <supplied reason="subaudible">il souffre</supplied> aux enfers avec sept générations de sa famille.</p>
				 </div>
